{"tid":304230,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解同男朋友講叫佢買本書我要打我一巴.....","createTime":"2017-06-30T17:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T14:57:25.000Z","uid":19334,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de5678fc5a799a93ae975d071bcad79c6f516213","tid":304230,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"話說小妹同男朋友拍都一段日子，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下個禮拜佢book左山頂間restaurant，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打算慶祝一個月快樂，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁慶祝就要送禮物架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔同既女仔，對禮物都會有唔同既要求。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而近年既港男送禮恩物，絕對係Pandora。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 但小妹已經有多條啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以叫佢不如買本書比我啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我地都有follow開大大與小妹（真人識），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/010459_a810740a8378ad7947d77f0f63efb0f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F010459_a810740a8378ad7947d77f0f63efb0f2.jpg&h=b8d43fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我叫佢買囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢發哂癲咁鬧我，話我唔知買黎做乜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要無啦啦車左我一巴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好唔好同佢分手好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8b42fc053f770fd3717e7b45cc00f0f9c49e7a","tid":304230,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:26:22.000Z","msg":"而家啲90後真係好無品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aacc2ec4064cec028ed4578111b4fbf9974946","tid":304230,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f49c1b60a651215e527ae5639eb627c58713d9","tid":304230,"uid":76831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:16:35.000Z","msg":"重作啦"},{"pid":"cc170ad5a9e8d72517a45c69a4517e3aeb2eec64","tid":304230,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家啲90後真係好無品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n郁d就動武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  eq低到"},{"pid":"f29d69029e65085991354bd3e4d310ec4aedb701","tid":304230,"uid":17578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"吉魯sir咁夜都唔瞓？"},{"pid":"dc0a91f6db5b7e1cee28bfa323074d7d1e229ec7","tid":304230,"uid":15015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"依家啲90後睇埋啲垃圾插畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5886485c8a3b2b46a25cef86aac23e52ee462955","tid":304230,"uid":123170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:07:56.000Z","msg":"唔係話針對幾多十後<br />\n不過永遠有問題嘅都係d 90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0feeb379ee9e7878f666edc25025736b